org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world

Interface HandlerPriorityRule

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HandlerPriorityRuleImpl

    public interface HandlerPriorityRule
    A representation of the model object 'Handler Priority Rule'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Order
    • Factory Id
    • Configuration Filter
    • Priority
    • Description

    See Also:
    WorldPackage.getHandlerPriorityRule()
